---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI 情报日报 | Synapse Daily Intelligence">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#FCAD2A] uppercase mb-4">DAILY INTELLIGENCE</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">AI 技术情报日报</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-lg mb-6">每天由 Synapse AI 团队自动生成 — 从海量 AI 动态中筛选出对企业管理者有实践价值的内容。</p>

    <!-- Intelligence report preview -->
    <div class="mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[var(--color-border)] shadow-md">
      <div class="bg-[#f0f0f0] px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5"><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></div></div>
        <div class="flex-1 mx-3"><div class="bg-white rounded px-3 py-0.5 text-[10px] text-[#999] text-center">synapse — daily AI intelligence report</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0A1628] p-5">
        <div class="text-xs text-[#FCAD2A] font-mono mb-3">SYNAPSE DAILY INTELLIGENCE · 2026-04-12</div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#0A1628] bg-[#FCAD2A] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Harness Engineering 正式成为 2026 AI 工程新范式</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-white bg-[#028CDC] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">MED</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Multi-Agent 系统企业采用量增长 327%</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#0A1628] bg-[#FCAD2A] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Claude Code Scheduled Tasks 全面可用</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono">Reviewed by Graphify Think Tank · 3 findings · 2 high priority</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">情报是怎么生成的？</h2>
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] leading-loose">
        <p><span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-semibold">8:00am</span> ── AI 技术研究员自动搜索 5 大 AI 前沿领域</p>
        <p><span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-semibold">筛选</span> ──── 4 个标准过滤（实践可行/价值明确/成本可控/场景匹配）</p>
        <p><span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-semibold">评审</span> ──── 智囊团内部审查（战略/决策/趋势三视角）</p>
        <p><span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-semibold">产出</span> ──── 3-5 条精华发现 + 行动建议 + 当前工作关联分析</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">追踪领域</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">Claude / Anthropic</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Claude Code 更新、新功能、API变化</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">AI Agent 框架</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">CrewAI / LangGraph / AutoGen</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">Harness Engineering</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Context Engineering 最佳实践</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">AI 开发工具</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Cursor / Claude Code / Copilot</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">企业 AI 落地</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">真实效率提升案例</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow"><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm">行业趋势</h3><p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">PropTech / 建筑AI / 市场动态</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[var(--color-dark)] rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">想要定制你的行业情报？</h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mb-4">Synapse 咨询客户可获得行业定制版每日情报服务。</p>
      <a href="/services" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold text-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">了解咨询服务</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
